<item>
            <title>[LU-2512] b1_8 and b2_1 test scripts fail against 2_3 and master server</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-2512</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The b1_8 and b2_1 scripts do not provide the index parameter for mkfs and so fail against a b2_3 or later server (I have not explore 2_2)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Example failed runs are here;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/2a20a39c-4a6f-11e2-8a7b-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/2a20a39c-4a6f-11e2-8a7b-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/3ff1522e-49df-11e2-bef8-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/3ff1522e-49df-11e2-bef8-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The key in the lustre initialisation being&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;21:30:56:Format ost1: /dev/lvm-OSS/P1
21:30:56:CMD: client-21-ib grep -c /mnt/ost1&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos; &apos;&lt;/span&gt; /proc/mounts
21:30:56:CMD: client-21-ib lsmod | grep lnet &amp;gt; /dev/&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;null&lt;/span&gt; &amp;amp;&amp;amp; lctl dl | grep &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos; ST &apos;&lt;/span&gt;
21:30:56:CMD: client-21-ib /usr/sbin/mkfs.lustre --ost --fsname=lustre --param sys.timeout=20 --device-size=2097152 --mgsnode=client-20-ib@o2ib --backfstype ldiskfs --reformat /dev/lvm-OSS/P1
21:30:56:client-21-ib: warning: /dev/lvm-OSS/P1: &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; Lustre 2.4 and later, the target index must be specified with --index
21:30:56:
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
