                            <comment id="49534" author="adilger" created="Fri, 21 Dec 2012 04:05:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This is the problem reported in &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1526&quot; title=&quot;interop 1.8,2.1 -&amp;gt; 2.4 &amp;quot;mkfs.lustre FATAL: The target index must be specified with --index&amp;quot;&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-1526&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-1526&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; already, and is one of the reasons why I&apos;d like to be testing interop against b2_1 and b1_8 instead of 2.1.3 and 1.8.8, respectively.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
